<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.239395>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Location of the collection sites of Desmacella species from Brazil. (1) Desmacella microsigmata sp. nov. (Rio Grande do Norte State); (2) Desmacella tylovariabilis sp. nov. (Rio de Janeiro State); (3) Desmacella annexa (São Paulo State)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/239395/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.239396>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Desmacella microsigmata sp. nov. (UFPEPOR 1759) in SEM. A, preserved specimen; B, thick section showing the ectosome and choanosome; C, size variation of tylostyles; D, sigma; E, details of microspines on the tip of a sigma; F, variation of tylostyle bases. Scale bars: A = 1 cm; B = 200 µm; C = 100 µm; D = 5 µm; E = 2 µm; F = 10 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/239396/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

